title: Westbrook's clutch plays seal Nuggets' rally in OT
description: Russell Westbrook came up big at the end of regulation and again in overtime for the Nuggets, who roared back from a 15-point deficit to beat the Clippers 112-110 in overtime in Game 1.

title: Pacers eye improvements after blowing out Bucks
description: The Pacers pointed to the things they could still do better after a comfortable win over the Bucks in Game 1 on Saturday.
author: Stephen Holder

title: Crucible curse? Reigning champion Wilson loses to Lei
description: Debutant Lei Peifan stuns defending champion Kyren Wilson by fighting back from 6-2 down to triumph 10-9 as the 'Crucible curse' strikes again.

title: 'Fuming' Watkins channelled 'anger' into 'dynamite' display
description: Ollie Watkins has a message for his manager Unai Emery - he wants to start the biggest games after inspiring Aston Villa to victory over Newcastle.

title: USF lands 3-star IMG safety Amari Jones
description: IMG Academy three-star safety Amari Jones won't have far to go when he starts college after committing to South Florida

title: Verstappen claims stunning Saudi pole after Norris crashes
description: Max Verstappen took a stunning pole position after championship leader Lando Norris crashed out in a dramatic qualifying session for the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix.

title: 'I've let myself down' - Norris stands by 'idiot' rebuke after crash
description: Lando Norris stood by his description of himself as an "idiot" for crashing in qualifying at the Saudi Arabian Grand Prix, saying he had let McLaren down and now needed a "bit of luck" to even salvage a top-five race result.
